---
description: "Container-only: Playwright must run via docker compose e2e service"
alwaysApply: true
---

Policy:
- Never run Playwright on the host.
- All Playwright commands MUST be executed via:
  - docker compose run --rm e2e <command>

If Playwright cannot run due to missing compose service or missing deps:
- Create a Lane I task to fix container setup.
- Do not fall back to host execution.